OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fheavy showers will gradually die out
OL,7,Fthis evening, leaving the rest of the
OL,8,Fnight largely dry with a few clear
OL,9,Fspells developing. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA mainly dry, bright
OL,12,Fmorning. Turning overcast through the
OL,13,Fafternoon as a band of occasionally
OL,14,Fheavy rain spreads in from the west.
OL,15,FFreshening afternoon winds,
OL,16,Foccasionally strong in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
